  <name>Race Sim - Gravel Race Simulation - 3 - 110min - RPE6-7</name>
  <description>Gravel Race Simulation — level 3

WARM-UP:
-10min ramp 50%-&gt;65% FTP (RPE 2-3)

MAIN SET:
-6min @ 63%-73% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 85-95rpm)
-1min @ 102%-108% FTP (Z4, RPE 6-7, 85-95rpm)
