-1min @ 102%-108% FTP (Z4, RPE 6-7, 85-95rpm)
-6min @ 63%-73% FTP (Z2, RPE 2-3, 85-95rpm)

COOL-DOWN:
-10min spin-down 70%-&gt;50% FTP (RPE 2-3)

HOW TO RIDE IT:
-Hold target on the efforts even on tired legs. Keep eating.

DIMENSIONS:
-zones Z2-Z4 · normal cadence · seated · rolling/mixed · attack/recover surges

FUEL:
-60-90g carbs/hr.</description>
